<section id="To_view_and_compare_genealogy" remap="TID_15187">
	<title>Comparing Genealogy of a Virtual Machine or Template</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To View and Compare Genealogy</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Infrastructure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Virtual Machines</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the accordion for the item to view genealogy.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click on the item to view its <guilabel>Summary</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				From the <guilabel>Relationships</guilabel> area in the <guilabel>Summary</guilabel>, click <guibutton>Genealogy</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Check the items to compare.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2148.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Compare Selected VMs)</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				For more information on the <guilabel>Compare</guilabel> feature, see <xref linkend="sect-Comparing_Virtual_Machines_and_Templates" />.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>